OL,6,FLimiting what new drivers can do on
OL,7,Fthe road will cut "needless deaths",
OL,8,Fministers have been told.
OL,10,FThe AA said motorists should be
OL,11,Fprevented from carrying passengers of
OL,12,Fa similar age for at least six months
OL,13,Fafter passing their test.
OL,15,FIt also called for to be required to
OL,16,Fkeep a record showing they have driven
OL,17,Fon all types of roads.
