OL,6,FThese limitations would form part of
OL,7,Fgraduated driving licences, which on
OL,8,Fdrivers for a set period after they
OL,9,Fpass their test.
OL,11,FThey are used in several countries
OL,12,Fincluding the US, Canada, Australia
OL,13,Fand Sweden.
OL,15,FThe Department for Transport (DfT)
OL,16,Fannounced in July 2019 it was
OL,17,Fconsidering introducing the licences
OL,18,Fin England.
