OL,6,FBut the assessment was halted in
OL,7,Fautumn 2020, partly due to the
OL,8,Fpotential impact on young people's
OL,9,Femployment.
OL,11,FAA president Edmund King said: "One of
OL,12,Fthe major issues that needs to be
OL,13,Faddressed is the needless deaths of
OL,14,Fyoung drivers, their passengers and
OL,15,Fothers caught up in these crashes.
OL,17,F"Each year nearly 5,000 people are
OL,18,Fkilled or seriously injured in crashes
OL,19,Finvolving at least one young driver.
