OL,6,FSharron Huddleston, whose 18-year-old
OL,7,Fdaughter Caitlin died as a passenger
OL,8,Fin a car crash in Cumbria in 2017, has
OL,9,Fformed Forget-me-not Families Uniting,
OL,10,Fa campaign group for people who have
OL,11,Flost loved ones in road collisions.
OL,13,FShe said: "Graduated licences are a
OL,14,Fcrucial issue. How many more young
OL,15,Fpeople need to die before action is
OL,16,Ftaken?
OL,18,F"We can't sit back any longer and just
OL,19,Fwatch as more and more young people
OL,20,Fare killed or seriously injured in
OL,21,Froad collisions.
